examples.korean: Its Arabic name, 'Harakat al-Muqawama al-Islamiya,' means Islamic Resistance Movement in English. 발음듣기 하마스의 아랍식 이름인 '하라캇 알 무카와마 알-이슬라미야,'는 영어로는 이슬람 저항운동을 의미한다. Neungyule
examples.english: Its Arabic name, 'Harakat al-Muqawama al-Islamiya,' means Islamic Resistance Movement in English. 발음

examples.korean: Hamas (in Arabic, an acronym for "Harakat Al-Muqawama Al-Islamia" - Islamic Resistance Movement - and a word meaning courage and bravery) is a Palestinian Islamic socio-political organization, which includes both military and political wings. 발음듣기 이슬람 저항 운동을 뜻하는 아랍어인 "하라캇 알-무카와마 알-이스라미아"의 약자이고 용기와 용감함을 뜻하는 단어인 하마스는 군사와 정치 조직 두 가지를 포함하고 있는 팔레스타인 이슬람 사회-정치 조직이다. EDU TIMES
examples.english: Hamas (in Arabic, an acronym for "Harakat Al-Muqawama Al-Islamia" - Islamic Resistance Movement - and a word meaning courage and bravery) is a Palestinian Islamic socio-political organization, which includes both military and political wings. 발음
